<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="content-strip primary">
      <div class="content-strip-inner">
        <h4 class="strip-title">修正課程用書</h4>
        <p class="strip-description"></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row row-inner-m">
    <div class="col m12 s12">
      <div class="groupon-field">
        <div class="groupon-field-inner">
          <div class="groupleader-form">
            <p>在這裏，您可以幫我們修正有問題的課程用書資料，首先選擇要修改的課，然後選擇一本新的書，確認後按下更新即可。此外，為了感謝您的協助，我們也會給您 NT$ 50 的折扣金來購買該書。</p>
            <p>&nbsp;</p>
            <span class="under-line-title">修改課程＆用書資料</span>
            <%= simple_form_for @course_book, url: user_course_books_path do |f| %>
              <%= react_component 'UserEditCourseBook', course_ucode: @course_book.course_ucode, book_isbn: @course_book.book_isbn %>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<script>
  $('.datepicker').pickadate({
    selectMonths: true, // Creates a dropdown to control month
    selectYears: 2 // Creates a dropdown of 15 years to control year
  });
  $(document).ready(function() {
    $('select').material_select();
  });
</script>
